==English==
===Noun===
'''tackle''' 
# (''sports'') a play where a player attempts to take control over the ball from an opponent, as in [[rugby]] or [[football]]
# {{fb}} a play where a defender brings the ball carrier to the ground
# {{slang}} [[penis]]
# (''fishing'') [[Bait]] used to [[lure]] [[fish]] to the [[hook]]
#{{fb}} The offensive positions between each [[guard]] and [[end]], [[offensive tackle]]
#{{fb}} The defensive positions between two [[end]]s, [[defensive tackle]]

